  <brief_title>ICU Cell Saver to Reduce Blood Transfusions in Cardiac</brief_title>
  <official_title>Routinely Use of CardioPAT Cell Saver in Cardiac Surgery: A Prospective Randomized Study Focused on Allogenic Blood Transfusion and Clinical Outcome</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Cardiochirurgia E.H.</agency>
